Even simple feedback helps a lot.

---

## Why I made this

I’m still learning too.  
This project exists because I believe the best way to grow in cybersecurity is to **build things and share them**.

If this tool helps even a few people save time or learn something new, then it’s already worth it.

Thanks for checking it out.

